OL,3,CWhat is the 'Viking Row' and why has
OL,4,Cit gone viral at the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FNorway fans have gone viral for their
OL,7,F'Viking row' celebration
OL,9,FNorway has had a successful World Cup
OL,10,Fso far, beating Iraq 4-1 in their
OL,11,Fopening match last week, and winning 3-
OL,12,F2 against Senegal on Monday to book
OL,13,Ftheir place in the last 32 of the
OL,14,Ftournament.
OL,16,FFans across the globe have celebrated
OL,17,Fthe team's performance, and not in the
OL,18,Fway that you might expect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
