OL,3,CWhat is the 'Viking Row' and why has
OL,4,Cit gone viral at the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FLarge groups were spotted across the
OL,7,FUnited States performing the 'Viking
OL,8,FRow', a seated movement that mimics
OL,9,Frowing a ship to the beat of a drum,
OL,10,Fin the style of Iceland's famous 2017
OL,11,F'Viking Clap'.
OL,13,FAfter the win against Senegal on
OL,14,FMonday, Norwegian striker Erling
OL,15,FHaaland, the team's top scorer,
OL,16,Fencouraged teammates to sit down on
OL,17,Fthe pitch and do the Viking Row while
OL,18,Fhe banged on a drum in celebration.
OL,20,FHaaland had earlier told Fox Sports
OL,21,Fthat he was a huge fan of the chant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
