OL,3,CWhat is the 'Viking Row' and why has
OL,4,Cit gone viral at the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,F"I saw it online; it's gone completely
OL,7,Fviral," Haaland told Fox Sports.
OL,8,F"Martin (Odegaard) asked me before the
OL,9,Fgame: 'Do you think we should join
OL,10,Fin?' I said, 'If we win, let's do it,
OL,11,Fwhy not?'"
OL,13,FBut where did this move come from?
OL,15,FSuperfan Ole Froystad, also known as
OL,16,FMr Row on social media, claims to have
OL,17,Ffounded this new tradition.
OL,26,@pD@IpmpD@JotpD@RpnwD@Po|
