OL,3,CWhat is the 'Viking Row' and why has
OL,4,Cit gone viral at the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FSpeaking to CBS, he said that the
OL,7,Fmotion is similar to what the Vikings
OL,8,Fwould have done as they sailed their
OL,9,Fships into the shore before battle.
OL,11,FFroystad has taken his trend from
OL,12,FBoston to Times Square in New York,
OL,13,Frepeatedly banging a drum and chanting
OL,14,F"row" to the crowd.
OL,16,FDescribing the atmosphere in Boston to
OL,17,FCBS, he said everyone was "hugging,
OL,18,Fpartying, jumping and rowing".
