OL,3,CWhat is the 'Viking Row' and why has
OL,4,Cit gone viral at the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FThe trend is now so widespread that
OL,7,Fpoliticians were spotted doing the
OL,8,F'Viking row' in Norway's parliament.
OL,10,FNorway fans aren't the only ones
OL,11,Fgaining publicity for their actions
OL,12,Fthis World Cup.
OL,14,FThe Tartan Army have become famous not
OL,15,Fonly for their bagpipes, but for their
OL,16,Fability to drink Boston pubs dry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
