OL,3,CWhat is the 'Viking Row' and why has
OL,4,Cit gone viral at the 2026 World Cup?
OL,6,FDutch supporters, known as the Orange
OL,7,FLegion, have also gone viral for their
OL,8,Fgroup dance, which involves jumping
OL,9,Fside to side to the Snollebollekes
OL,10,Ftune Links Rechts, which translates to
OL,11,F'Left Right'.
OL,13,FNorway fans could have the opportunity
OL,14,Fto showcase their rowing form again on
OL,15,FFriday, as the team is due to face
OL,16,FFrance.
OL,18,FWhether they'll row their way to the
OL,19,Ffinal or back home to Norway is yet to
OL,20,Fbe determined.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
